      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a major project or a source for parts. The engine requires significant mechanical attention to be reliable, and the transmission shows signs of slipping. Externally, the body has several large dents, peeling clear coat, and visible rust bubbling along the wheel arches and rocker panels. The interior is heavily worn with torn upholstery and some non-functional electronics. Please expect to invest considerable time and resources to get this car back on the road.",
