      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. Every aspect of this car has been meticulously maintained, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that still smells new. Mechanically, it is perfect, with a complete service history and no signs of wear or mechanical aging. For the discerning buyer who demands perfection, this car offers a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been kept in climate-controlled storage and treated with the utmost care. It is ready to be driven or added to a collection without any further investment required.",
