    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project seekers! This vehicle is looking for a new home where it can get the attention it deserves. While it currently needs some mechanical and cosmetic work, it serves as a fantastic foundation for a restoration project or a reliable source for parts. It's an incredible opportunity to get behind the wheel at a budget-friendly price point!",
