    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for checking out my listing! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car, and I think you're going to love it. It\u2019s been a fantastic ride and is still in really solid shape\u2014perfect for someone who wants a reliable daily driver that looks great and feels even better behind the wheel. It\u2019s been well-cared for and is totally ready for its next road trip or commute. I\u2019d love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see for yourself! Feel free to shoot me any questions you have\u2014I'm happy to chat!",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 engine and a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox. This example boasts a linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline, supported by recent preventative maintenance including rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators. The chassis retains its precision via Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and the factory M-Variable locking differential, providing exceptional turn-in and rear-axle feedback. While the exterior shows minor stone chips and light patina commensurate with enthusiast use, the subframe has been inspected and the bushings remain tight. A well-sorted, driver-focused machine with a clean oil analysis history.",
      "price": 36850.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Used vehicle in good condition. Maintenance records up to date. Clean title. Reliable performance with minor cosmetic wear.",
